The sched_pert program is a small application based on opm-common to perturbe
schedule rates.

1. opm-common

You need a very recent version of opm-common installed, you can use the script
install-opm.sgh to install opm-common. The script will download opm-common from
github and build and install the opm common libraries in opm/install


2. Build sched_pert

mkdir build
cd build
cmake ../ -DCMAKE_PREFIX_PATH=${PWD}/../opm/install
make


3. Run the script

sched_pert ECLIPSE.DATA

